@startuml C4_Integrity_Verification_Sequence

title C4 - Sequence: Verifica Integrita e propagazione stati (compatta)

autonumber
hide footbox
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 80

actor Renderer as UI
participant "CheckIntegrityIpcAdapter" as IPC
participant "CheckIntegrityUC" as UC
participant "IntegrityVerificationService" as VerifySvc
participant "Repo Layer" as Repo
participant "SqliteTransactionManager" as Tx
participant "HashingService" as Hash

UI -> IPC: invoke(check-integrity:*, id)
IPC -> UC: execute(id)
UC -> VerifySvc: checkIntegrity(level, id)

VerifySvc -> Tx: runInTransaction(work)
activate Tx
Tx -> VerifySvc: BEGIN IMMEDIATE

VerifySvc -> VerifySvc: resolveRoot(level, id)
loop per node in subtree (bottom-up)
  VerifySvc -> Repo: getChildren(level, nodeId)
  alt node is FILE
    VerifySvc -> Hash: checkFileIntegrity(path, expectedHash)
    Hash --> VerifySvc: VALID | INVALID
  else node is aggregate
    VerifySvc -> VerifySvc: aggregateStatuses(children)
  end
  VerifySvc -> Repo: updateIntegrityStatus(level, nodeId, status)
end

Tx -> VerifySvc: COMMIT
VerifySvc --> UC: IntegrityStatusEnum
UC --> IPC: IntegrityStatusEnum
IPC --> UI: IntegrityStatusEnum

deactivate Tx

note over VerifySvc, Tx
If root is missing or any runtime error occurs:
- transaction is rolled back
- IPC returns INTEGRITY_VERIFY_ERROR
end note

note right of VerifySvc
  aggregateStatuses rules:
  1) no children -> VALID
  2) any INVALID -> INVALID
  3) else, any UNKNOWN -> UNKNOWN
  4) else -> VALID
end note

@enduml
